[POPPY BARKS]

584
00:42:57,825 --> 00:42:59,367
[GASPS]

585
00:43:06,792 --> 00:43:08,167
[SPEAKS IN ALIEN LANGUAGE]

586
00:43:31,900 --> 00:43:34,527
Holy mother of God.

587
00:43:34,695 --> 00:43:35,820
Did you see that?

588
00:43:35,988 --> 00:43:38,615
We should hit these assholes
