680
00:50:22,477 --> 00:50:23,644
Yeah.

681
00:50:23,812 --> 00:50:27,481
- Give me your ma again, all right?
- All right. Hold on. Mom.

682
00:50:27,649 --> 00:50:30,818
- You always get to the phone first.
