1131
01:37:44,233 --> 01:37:46,484
I prepared a speech. Is that all right?

1132
01:37:47,570 --> 01:37:49,320
Sure, that's very appropriate.

1133
01:37:54,201 --> 01:37:56,077
Hi, everybody.

